 <title xml:id="HardwareServices">Disable Bluetooth Input Devices Daemon</title>
 <para>
  If the system has no Bluetooth input devices (e.g., wireless keyboard
  or mouse), disable this daemon.
  <indexterm>
   <primary>Bluetooth</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <indexterm>
   <primary>hidd</primary>
  </indexterm>
 </para>
